Sentencas: An anode supported solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with a dual layer anode consisting of a Cu-CeO2 impregnated Ni-yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) support outer layer and a Ni-YSZ electroactive inner layer was investigated for the direct operation on ethanol.
Titulo: High-Performance Direct Ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: High electrochemical performance without evidence of anode coking was demonstrated at 800 degrees C in short term tests.
Titulo: High-Performance Direct Ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: A peak power density of about 400 mW/cm(2) was obtained with 7.3% ethanol balance He fuel and air oxidant.
Titulo: High-Performance Direct Ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
